<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You’ve Been Added as a Staff Member</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 30px 25px;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0369A0 0%, #29BCB7 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 60px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .invite-box {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(171.9deg, #FFFFFF 29.33%, #E5F7FF 80.2%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .invite-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0369A0 0%, #29BCB7 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .email-container {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRwJromFWFHBKmfdiQjQLo5iqIv8RLPJJKutA&s">
    </div>

    <h1 class="gradient-text">You’ve Been Added as a Staff Member</h1>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <span class="highlight"><%= staff.fullName %></span>,</p>

        <p>You have been added as a <span class="highlight"><%= staff.title %></span> to the account <span class="highlight"><%= companyName %></span>.</p>

        <p>You can now access the system and begin managing your assigned responsibilities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="invite-box">
        <p><strong>Activate Your Staff Access</strong></p>
        <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" class="invite-btn">Access Account</a>
        <p style="margin-top:15px; font-size:13px; color:#666;">
            For security reasons, this link may expire after some time.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><span class="highlight">Was this unexpected?</span>
            If you believe you were added in error, please contact the account administrator immediately or ignore this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to your account administrator or reply to this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Inibyte Limited Team</strong></p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
